subtitle: Welcome to the third episode of "Different Aliens We Know Exist," where we delve into
the existence of various extraterrestrial beings that have visited or made contact with
planet earth, just like humanity, extraterrestrial beings can exhibit a spectrum of good or evil.
Recognizing this duality is imperative as we delve into confidential ufo files, spiritual
medium channels, and close encounters.
The Naacals, of the planet RAMAY, from a star system named Capella, in the auriga constellation.
They are short and bulky, with square jaws and elongated skull.
Their face features are similar to those of south American humans on earth but with a
smaller nose.
Their eyes are black, brown or dark grey stretched and slender, and they're slightly pointed
ears.
The naacals have been on earth even before the arrival of the annunaki but after the
PAA-TAAL.
They established Lemuria and helped the annunaki atlanteans of nibiru establish Atlantis.
After the wars with Selosii reached temporary domination of earth, The naacals refused to
bow down to the hierarchical selosi rule and formed the Yu empire, choosing to move underground.
Settling in the south and central American continents, they were at the origin of the
rise of the mayan civilization.
Considerably advanced in sciences, they taught the mayans about astronomy and time, and then
left AND DEPARTED FROM the mayan civilization.
The mayan people then started to perform blood sacrifices in their names, worshiping them
as gods.
The Naacals worked closely with the annunaki of nibiru, and helping build atlantis.
They are now apart of the galactic federation of worlds and our apart of the protection
programs on earth.
They practice inter dimensional travel and space, their ships are metallic silver and
bright.
The Laani are from the first planet Egoria of the Vega man system.
Unfortunately first in line when the massive draconian empire fleet approached.
They are tall humanoids with feline face features for the upper part of their head, from their
flat nose with noticeable nostrils, to their long heavy red or golden hair, although their
mouth is humanoid-like, as are the rest of their bodies.
Their ears are small and rounded, and they have a tail.
Their skin, generally light brown, is covered with a short silky fur and their eyes are
of all sorts of shades, amber and turquoise being the most common color.
Since the Lyran Orion Wars, they're kind has spread widely throughout the galaxy and they
are now true master of genetics, adapting their physiology to the new environments,
giving birth to a wide genetic diversity of features, as for instance the bird like mutation
in the carian system of orion.
The Laani and the sister breed Taali are naturally compatible and their cross breed is named
"Ayal".
Next, are the The Aramani Cetains from a planet named Araman, in the Tau Ceti system called
Norca, and their very name attests of their lyran ORIGIN: "Aramani" in the ancient lyran
common root language, means the exiled men humanoid.
The Aramani are a race of tan skinned 5 foot 5 tall humans with slightly pointed ears,
dark hair and strong muscular density.
They are genetically descendant of the lyran Taal race, a mixed group of humanoid who fled
the attack of their world by the DRACO empire.
They developed a fair civilization which principles are based on justice.
Not eager to conquests, aramani have interest in earth only for scientific curiosity and
by duty to the galactic federation of worlds, to whom they are affiliated.
In alliance with the annunaki of nibru and later annunaki pleiadeans, as well as with
other annunaki societies who have been victims of the reptilian collective, they collaborated
to the establishment of a common defense against their reptilian nemesis.
They visit earth only when in collaboration with the work of the galactic federation of
worlds, whose main work is to raise the awareness of the earthlings about the subversion of
their societies by other races, notably the draconians, maytra and kiily tokurt helping
them identify and expose corrupt institutions and elites manipulation in liaison with these
enemies, uplifting human consciousness and developing strategies against advanced mind
control technologies, monitoring extraterrestrial infiltration, deprogramming mind control rescuing
abductees and implant removal.
It is known that they were rewarded by the annuanki royals of nibiru to genetically mark
and rule a people during the genetic engineering of homo sapien sapien.
Their ships are discoidal and of a very pristine shape.
The Afim Spiantsy are from the planet Afiola, in the star system Aldoram.
They have blue skin covered with blue spots, darker for males and lighter for females,
with stretched eyes angled upwards.
Afim Spiantsy are of smaller stature than earth humans and they not need oxygen, largest
percentage of their planet's atmosphere in hydrogen.
Their real name Afim, but they call themselves Afim Spiantsy because of a war they won against
the Spiantsy race, 12 times more numerous with 35 more ships and resources than Afim.
Their name on it's own is a warning to other races.
Afim Society is based on a warrior patriarchy structure and although they developed space
travel and technology, thanks to the help of selosii and lyrans, their culture is still
an early one.
This is a good example of premature intercultural contact.
They colonized 10 planets in non-violent ways but Afim have no desire of conquest on Terra,
aware to be outnumbered by the forces of the galactic federation which they are part of
and the of the reptilian Orion alliance.
They are an observing race.
Their technology is so advanced and developed THAT they can travel to earth within 20 earth
minutes.
They visit earth to study human deviation.
When they are close to humans...
they can become invisible if they don't wish to be seen.....
They can be found in in mainly places of deviance such as entertainment facilities....
mental hospitals..... and even music festivals.
Their ships are small and spherical, metallic aspect, and silver with a transversal band
of windows and lights.
They know warp speed and space bending.
The next extraterrestrial species to mention is the Canis, originating from the star system
Canis Major.
These beings are canine aliens hailing from the Planet New two , where they preside over
a significant expanse of their star system.
Renowned for their peaceful nature, sophistication, and advanced technology, the Canis possess
humanoid bodies adorned with countless variety of canine and human like facial features creating
an interesting human dog hybrid.
Standing at impressive heights of either 4 to 6 feet feet walking upright, they are esteemed
members of the galactic alliance always well groomed, and usually wearing luxurious long
robes and many are also hired skilled mercenaries and technical engineers.
They have octagonal ships.
Of particular interest is their fascination with humans, largely due to the human practice
of keeping canines as pets.
It's speculated that their ancestors played a role in the evolution of planet Earth's
canines during the seeding of Tiamat, particularly the gray wolf.
It is also important to know this is where the term of werewolves and Skinwalkers began.
A race of dog people.
Despite evolving differently over millions of years, influenced by draconian interbreeding
programs, the Canis species maintain a close genetic connection to Earth's canine species.
Additionally, they also have a penchant for keeping other mammals, such as monkeys, as
pets in their OWN society.
The Orela originate from the Ophiuchus constellation, and are part of the council of five.
Tall grey beings, very slim, Orelai have a high thin long neck, a triangular face with
a slit for the mouth, barely visible nostrils, and slanted eyes with pupil.
They are very old, very wise, and ambassadors for peace in the high council of the galactic
federation of the worlds.
They have two genders, but do not copulate for reproduction anymore, as this function
became inefficient with their evolution.
They now "fabricate" new organic individual bodies and imbue in it soul from their matrix.
an awe-inspiring utopian city nestled amidst verdant landscapes where flora intertwines
gracefully with the magnificent architecture reminiscent of ancient Greek design.
Here, in this advanced civilization crafted by the hands of an extraterrestrial race,
technology and nature coalesce harmoniously to create a realm of unparalleled beauty and
serenity.
peace reigns supreme, and democracy flourishes in its purest form.
Every voice is heard, and every opinion is valued, as the citizens of Ophiuchus system
come together to govern themselves with wisdom and compassion.
Conflict is virtually unknown, replaced instead by a collective desire to nurture and protect
the precious gift of life They have round, flat ships, but rarely ever travel out of
their world, as they perform instead inter dimensional resonance.
The Alcobata are located on the planet Urdam II, in the Goraneor system, which is their
original world but their race had extended far out in this galaxy and unfortunately beyond.
Alcobata have five bony points sticking out of top of their skull....
They are extremely aggressive and considered by the galactic federation of worlds as a
parasite race....
They are a warrior class based society and very complex in it's hierarchical structure.
Their religious system is also very complicated with a myriad of gods.....
They breed by eggs or by mammal way as there are two ways of reproduction.....
They have androgynous ability and can inseminate themselves when chosen time has come.
For this transformation, they produce a particular hormone which will activate the reproductive
function.....
The offspring from the eggs and the offspring from the womb biologically have different
purposes in the society.
Females procreate by womb individuals assigned to practical social and political roles of
both genders.
The offspring from eggs, predominantly males, are fit to be warriors and are particularly
aggressive.
The Alcobata have colonized 200 planets currently.
Frequent and ongoing abductions of humans..... a practice they perform on all their colonized
worlds, purpose unknown but suspected slavery.
They do not like to interact with other alien races.
They are very aggressive hostile civilization.
They are suspected to have been involved in several plane crashes, the most case known
was the Korean airlines flight 007 over Russia in 1983.
The Russians took and accepted the blame for it.
Last sighting was in Canada in September 2001.
Alcobata have 5000 ships Their ships are very fast and their space travel technology has
made them one of the most dangerous races, as they can move very fast.
The Kaai species are pacifist reptilian fish hybrids that are well involved in galactic
diplomacy.
Their world is luxuriant with life and the abundance of resources could have attracted
the attention of some malevolent empires, if the haze of acidic clouds surrounding their
world had not discouraged them to chance an assault.
Kaai Reptiloids strive on a very rare environment which particular conditions wouldn't suit
the two thirds of all other species in the galaxy, and they can leave their world to
travel only in environmental suits and ships made with a very particular metal.
Kaai cannot breathe any other air than theirs; the federation's breathing implant's range
does not work on them.
The vegetation of the Kaai planet is unlike anything seen on Earth, with flora that seems
to glow with an otherworldly luminescence, casting a soft, iridescent glow over the entire
cityscape.
Trees with branches that reach towards the heavens sway gently in the breeze, their leaves
shimmering like precious gems in the sunlight.
It's not just the breathtaking scenery that captivates the senses on the planet.
The inhabitants of this celestial haven are as remarkable as the world they inhabit.
Possessing technology on par with that of humanity, they have chosen to harness its
power not for conquest or dominance, but for the betterment of society and the preservation
of their harmonious way of life.
Next are the Indugutk, who are extremely violent.
Their home world is Urrud Prime, an artificially engineered planet in the Bellatrix system.
Indugtks are saurian-reptiloids native to Uruud.
They are extremely violent in nature and look like tall white reptiloid greys.
They have a narrow wrinkled face with elongated skull, a large mouth, thick brow ridge and
very long neck.
They do not wear clothing.
You can recognize them by this specific smell they produce, before even seeing them, and
which reminds of burnt Sulphur.
Indugtk have treaties with the earth's government involved in space programs such as US, Russia
and China for they have bases on the moon for mining using slaves from all galaxies
for this chore.
Next, The Janosians are a small Atlantean royal colony of the ancient princess Ninhursag
or Ninmah of Nibiru, sharing her gray and reptilian heritage with elongated skulls,
African Asiatic features from dark red, yellowish pale, and blue skin mulattoe hybrids with
usually no hair or very dark long locks or straight hair, slimmer bodies compared to
the other Annunaki royal houses with muscular body features.
In the Atlantean language, it means "Outpost 361".
That tells how widely extended is their presence in this galaxy, and beyond.
This blue planet has 3 suns, 4 moons, and is subtropical temperate.
Terraformed, which doesn't surprise.
They are an exiled colony who left your solar system when their planet, Janos also known
as Marduk located between Mars and Jupiter, was pulverized by the Orion empire and Maytrei.
These beings made contact with Earth's psychic Maria Orsic in 1919, expressing themselves
in the ancient Earth language still in use by them known as Sumerian.
Interestingly, this group shares ancestors with the royal Adari house who were the gods
to ancient Hindu texts on earth.
Lastly, are the Airk of the constellation of Phiuchus near Yed Prior which is a three-planet
system.
They can live up to two thousand years.
Their height is similar to that of a normal human; they are vegetarian and considered
by other races as nice people, peaceful, much respected, and presumably having mystical
powers.
They have pale skin and big eyes with a round pupil.
No hair on females.
Females are slim, and their skin is nearly translucent.
They wear clothes, very comfortable; it is a sort of silk.
They don't breathe Earth's atmosphere and are not interested in settling.
Very good relationship with the galactic federation of worlds, which they are part of, but they
do not take part in planetary programs.
Four fingers and a thumb.
Small very tiny nose.
Ears quasi inexistent, just holes.
Sweet-smiling people.
They never stay long on Earth and do not interact with humans or other species.
They mostly use Earth as a stop to quickly gather something they may need before they
leave for their real destination.
They are mostly nocturnal and have been coming to Earth since at least 1000 AD.
They do not carry abductions.
Their ships emit a bright orange light, and most of them are octagonal.
